<div class="row" id="category_page">

	<div class="col-md-8">
		<article>
			<form action="/category/destroy/<%= category.id %>" method="POST" class="form-signin" id="edit-category-form">
				<h2 class="form-sigin-heading">Delete category</h2>
				<p>So you wanne delete the <strong><%= category.title %></strong> category?</p>
				<p>Check the checkbox to delete</p>
				<label>Confirm to delete '<%= category.title %>' category<input type="checkbox" name="confirmDelete" value="confirmDelete" ng-model='confirmDelete'></label>
				<input type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block" value="Delete category" ng-disabled="deleteButtonDisabled">
				<input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= _csrf %>">
			</form>
		</article>
	</div>	

	<div class="col-md-4">
		<aside>
			<h2>Delete category</h2>
		</aside>
	</div>

</div>